{
    "653:0": "atha ekonaviṃśaḥ paṭalavisaraḥ |",
    "653:1": "atha khalu bhagavān śākyamuniḥ punarapi śuddhāvāsabhavanamavalokya mañjuśriyaṃ kumārabhūtamāmantrayate sma ||",
    "653:2": "asti mañjuśrīḥ ! tṛtīyamapi jyotiṣajñānaniyamaparivartaṃ bhāṣiṣye pūrvakaiḥ samyak sambuddhairbhāṣitaṃ cābhyanumoditaṃ ca tvadīyamantratantrārthakalpitam |",
    "653:3": "śṛṇu sādhu ca suṣṭhu ca manasi kuru ||",
    "653:4": "evamukte bhagavatā śākyamuninā mañjuśrīḥ kumārabhūto bodhisattvo mahāsattvaḥ utthāyāsanādekāṃśamuttarāsaṅgaṃ kṛtvā,",
    "653:5": "dakṣiṇaṃ jānumaṇḍalaṃ pṛthivyāṃ pratiṣṭhāpya,",
    "653:6": "yena bhagavāṃ,",
    "653:7": "tenāñjaliṃ pragṛhya,",
    "653:8": "bhagavantametadavocat|",
    "653:9": "tat sādhu bhagavāṃ bhāṣatu jyotiṣajñānapaṭalavisaram |",
    "653:10": "tad bhaviṣyati sattvānāmarthāya hitāya sukhāya |",
    "653:11": "devamanuṣyāṇāṃ sarvamantracaryānupraviṣṭānāṃ ca sattvānāmanuttarāyāṃ samyak sambodho,",
    "653:12": "abhiprasthitānāṃ ca,",
    "653:13": "upāyakauśalyamantracaryā sukhena sādhayiṣyanti|",
    "653:14": "sarvasattvānukūlaṃ yogavidhānakarmānukūlaṃ kālaniyamaniṣyanditakarmasvakatāṃ nakṣatravāragrahayonikṣetrarāśisamodayām |",
    "653:15": "tad bhaviṣyati sukhasādhanopāyaṃ mantrānuvartanaṃ sukhavipākaṃ tad bhaviṣyati te bodhisattvānāṃ viṣpanditavikurvaṇa ṛddhyadhiṣṭhānam ||",
    "653:16": "evamukte mañjuśriyā kumārabhūtena atha bhagavāṃ mañjuśriyaṃ kumārabhūtametadavocat |",
    "653:17": "sādhu sādhu mañjuśrīḥ! yastathāgatametamarthaṃ paripṛcchase |",
    "653:18": "tena hi śṛṇu sādhu ca suṣṭhu ca manasi kuru |",
    "653:19": "bhāṣiṣye sarvasattvānāmarthāya ||",
    "653:20": "evamukte mañjuśrīḥ kumārabhūto bhagavataścaraṇayornipatya,",
    "653:21": "niṣaṇṇo dharmaśravaṇāya ||",
    "653:22": "atha bhagavāṃ sarvāvantaṃ śuddhāvāsabhavanamābhayā sphuritvā,",
    "653:23": "sarvabuddhāvalokanadyotanīṃ nāma samādhiṃ samāpadyate sma |",
    "653:24": "samanantarasamāpannasya bhagavataḥ kāyānnīlapītāvadātamāñjiṣṭhasphaṭikavarṇādayo raśmayo niścaranti sma |",
    "653:25": "nirgatya ca sattvānāṃ buddhakṣetrāṃ avabhāsya,",
    "653:26": "sarvāṇi ca grahanakṣatrayoniṃ samāśrayarāśitārāṃ bhavanānyavabhāsya,",
    "653:27": "gaganatalagatāṃ narakatiryakpretadevabhavanamanuṣyasarvasattvabhavanāni cāvabhāsya sarvaduḥkhāni ca pratiprasrabhya sarvasattvānāṃ punareva bhagavataḥ śākyamuneḥ kārye'ntarddhīyate sma ||",
    "653:28": "atha bhagavān śākyamunistasmāt samādhervyutthāya sarvāṃ tāṃ nakṣatragraharāśidevasaṅghānāmantrayate sma |",
    "653:29": "śṛṇvantu bhavantaḥ sarvanakṣatradevasaṅghāḥ ! yo hyasmin dharmavinaye mantracaryāyāṃ samanupraviṣṭa iha kalpavisare tat sādhayet sarvamantrāṇāṃ sarvadravyakarmavidhānādiṣu,",
    "653:30": "na bhavadbhistatra vighnaṃ kartavyaṃ sarvaireva sannipatitaiḥ rakṣāvidhānasānnidhyaṃ kathayitavyam |",
    "653:31": "yo hyenaṃ samayamatikramet,",
    "653:32": "tasya yamāntakaḥ krodharājā sarvanakṣatragrahāṇāṃ tatkṣaṇādevamaparyantalokadhātusthitānāṃ sasutānāṃ sabāndhavāṃ sapārṣadānānayati sma,",
    "653:33": "sarveṣāṃ ca mūrdhani sthitvā pādenākramya vividhāni krūrakarmaṛddhiprātihāryāṇi darśayati sma,",
    "653:34": "buddhādhiṣṭhānena prāṇairviyojayati sma,",
    "653:35": "samaye ca sthāpayati sma,",
    "653:36": "vikṛtarūpamātmānaṃ darśayati sma,",
    "653:37": "ante sarvabhūtayakṣarākṣasanakṣatragraharāśayo nisattvagaruḍamarutamahoragagaṇā sarvairbhītāstrastāḥ,",
    "653:38": "tharatharāyamānāḥ,",
    "653:39": "mahāvikrośaṃ kurvāṇaḥ bhagavataḥ pādayornipatya prakampyamānā evamāhuḥ - paritrāyasva bhagavan ! paritrāyasva |",
    "653:40": "sugata anāthāḥ sma,",
    "653:41": "atrāṇāḥ sma,",
    "653:42": "mahākrodharāja bhayabhītā jīvitaṃ no bhagavān samanuprayacchāsmākam |",
    "653:43": "ityevamuktvā tūṣṇīmbhūtāḥ pravepamānagātrāḥ ||",
    "653:44": "atha bhagavān śākyamuniḥ |",
    "653:45": "tāṃ nakṣatragrahasaṅghātāṃśca yakṣarākṣasapretapiśācamātaragaṇānāmantrayate sma |",
    "653:46": "mā bhaiṣṭatha mārṣāḥ ! bho bhaiṣṭatha mārṣāḥ ! nāsti athāgatānāmantika upasaṅkrāntānāṃ bhayaṃ vā maraṇaṃ vā |",
    "653:47": "sarvaduḥkhā nivāryo hi mārṣāḥ ! buddhaṃ śaraṇaṃ gacched,",
    "653:48": "vipadānāmagryaṃ dharmaṃ śaraṇaṃ gacched,",
    "653:49": "virāgāṇāmagryaṃ saṅghaṃ śaraṇaṃ gacched,",
    "653:50": "gaṇānāmagryaṃ na tasya bhavati lomaharṣam |",
    "653:51": "vāñchanti tattvo vākaḥ punarvādo mṛtyubhayaṃ sarvabhayaduḥkhebhyo mukta eva draṣṭavyaḥ |",
    "653:52": "sarvasāṃsārikaṃ bhayaṃ na kadācid vidyate |",
    "653:53": "duḥkhopaśamaṃ śāntiṃ nijvaraṃ sanniyataṃ bodhiparāyaṇaṃ padamavāpnuyāditi ||",
    "653:54": "atha tatkṣaṇādeva bhagavatā teṣāṃ sarvaduḥkhāni ṛddhyā pratipramugdhānīti yamāntakaśca krodharājā bhagavataścaraṇayornipatya,",
    "653:55": "mañjuśriyasya kumārabhūtasya samīpe sanniṣaṇṇo dharmaśravaṇāya ||",
    "653:56": "sarve ca te grahanakṣatragaṇāḥ sarvaduḥkhāni ca pratiprasrabhyante sma |",
    "653:57": "sarvaśca ketavo praśāntā niṣaṇṇāśca dharmaśravaṇāya svasthībhūtā ekāgramanaso bhagavantaṃ vyavalokamānā vismayotphullanayanā + dvilpamanasaśca saṃvṛttā abhūvaṃ ||",
    "653:58": "atha bhagavatā lokānukampārthaṃ tathā tathā dharmadeśanā kṛtā caturāryasatyasamprayuktā yathā yathā taiḥ sattvaiḥ kaiścit satyāni dṛṣṭāni kaiścidarhatvaṃ kṛtam,",
    "653:59": "kaiścit pratyekabodhaḥ,",
    "653:60": "kaiścidanuttarāyāṃ samyak sambodhau cittānyutpāditāni,",
    "653:61": "sarvaṃ ca niyatāvyākṛtānuttarāyāṃ samyak sambodhau,",
    "653:62": "sarvaiśca pithitānyapāpadurgativinipātāni devamanuṣyopapattau dvārāṇyutpāditāni,",
    "653:63": "svargārgalamapāvṛtam |",
    "653:64": "sarve ca samayamadhitiṣṭhanti ||",
    "653:65": "atha bhagavān śākyamunisteṣāmanuśayaṃ jñātvā,",
    "653:66": "vinayakālasamayamanantarameva teṣāṃ vinītāṃ sattvāṃ jñātvā,",
    "653:67": "dharmaṃ bhāṣate sma ||",
    "653:68": "ariduḥkhasamākrāntaṃ doṣajaṃ vinidhāśrayam |",
    "653:69": "abhāvo devagaṇāḥ sarve pṛjyante śāsane iha ||",
    "653:70": "ārabhadhvaṃ paraṃ vīryaṃ bodhisopānahetukam |",
    "653:71": "prāpnuyādeva saṅghātāḥ śāntanijvaramālayam ||",
    "653:72": "aśokaṃ virajaṃ kṣemaṃ nirvāṇaṃ vāpi naiṣṭhikam |",
    "653:73": "nirmalaṃ gaganatulyākhyaṃ abhāvaṃ tu svabhāvikam ||",
    "653:74": "paraṃ prāpsyathāninditaṃ divyaṃ sujuṣṭamanāvṛtam |",
    "653:75": "anityaduḥkhaśūnyārthamanātmaṃ tu samoditam ||",
    "653:76": "bhāvayanto divā sarvaṃ prāpsyante caiva naiṣṭhikamiti |",
    "653:77": "mantratantrābhidhānena caryā caiva sukhodayā ||",
    "653:78": "kathitā jinavaraiḥ śreṣṭhā mantrasiddhirudāhṛtā |",
    "653:79": "upāyaṃ sattvānāṃ agre niyogenaiva dhīmataiḥ ||",
    "653:80": "kathitā mantrasiddhistu phalakāle samodaye |",
    "653:81": "vicitraṃ karmaṇāṃ jāti vicitreva yojitā ||",
    "653:82": "vicitrā karmataḥ siddhirvicitraṃ karmayonijam |",
    "653:83": "vicitrā citrarūpeṇa mantrairebhirniyojitā ||",
    "653:84": "vicitrārthāḥ karmavistarā vicitraṃ karma ucyate |",
    "653:85": "karma cintyā tathā citraṃ acintyaṃ cāpi cintitam ||",
    "653:86": "tasmāt prārambhanmantrī mantracitreṣu puṣkalām |",
    "653:87": "rāśayaḥ kathitāścitrā teṣu jātā narā sadā ||",
    "653:88": "sadevāsuramukhyāstu vividhā prāṇivihaṅgamā |",
    "653:89": "teṣāṃ ca yāni cihnāni tāni siddhiṣu yojayet ||",
    "653:90": "meṣarāśau tathā jātaḥ manujā vā divaukasā |",
    "653:91": "bahvapatyo bahubhāṣyo surūpaścāpi jāyate ||",
    "653:92": "vaṇik śīlī tathā śūraḥ manujaḥ strīṣu varṇitaḥ |",
    "653:93": "vakro lubdhacittaśca bhūpatirgṛhasevinaḥ ||",
    "653:94": "tatrasthaścandramā proktaḥ sarvakarme prayojayet |",
    "653:95": "ādityo yadi dṛśyeta meparāśisamāśritaḥ ||",
    "653:96": "tatra karma sadā siddhi krūrakarmasuyojitām |",
    "653:97": "yānaṃ gamanaṃ caiva āsanaṃ śayanaṃ sadā ||",
    "653:98": "na bhajet tantramantrajño viruddhā sarvayogibhiḥ |",
    "653:99": "tatra jātaḥ sadā martyo mantraṃ deyābhicārukam ||",
    "653:100": "vṛṣarāśau tadā jāto manujo bhogavānsadā |",
    "653:101": "strīṣu kāntaḥ sadā lubdhaḥ dharmādharmavicārakaḥ ||",
    "653:102": "grāmyasevī sadādhyakṣo devarāṅgāni bodhatām |",
    "653:103": "tatrasthaścandramā jāto dhārmiko'sau sureśvaraḥ ||",
    "653:104": "bhavet tasya cittaṃ vai rājyamāśrayatā sadā |",
    "653:105": "tasya mantrā sadā deyā caityā jinabhāṣitaḥ ||",
    "653:106": "tena candrārthayuktenarāśrayo'rthanibodhitāḥ |",
    "653:107": "gamanāgamanaṃ karma smaśrukarma ca yuktimām ||",
    "653:108": "ācared grahakarmāṇi na kuryādyābhicārukam |",
    "653:109": "sarvakarmasamudyogaṃ mantrasiddhisukhodayam ||",
    "653:110": "ālikhenmaṇḍalādīnāṃ buddhabimbāṃśca kārayet |",
    "653:111": "siddhadravyasurāśreṣṭā sādhyamānā divaukasā ||",
    "653:112": "sidhyante mantribhiryuktā nakṣatreṣveva risiṣu |",
    "653:113": "mithunāyāṃ yadā jāto mānuṣo'tha divaukasaḥ ||",
    "653:114": "teṣāṃ ca gaticihnāni siddhikālaṃ nibodhatām |",
    "653:115": "āḍhyo udyuktacittaśca śaṭho mūrkho'tha jāyate ||",
    "653:116": "tatrastho yadi vikhyātaḥ nakṣatrā niśi bhūṣaṇam |",
    "653:117": "tataḥ kānto kavenmartyo bandhūnāṃ vallabhaḥ sadā ||",
    "653:118": "dhanāḍhyo yuktimantaśca maheśākhyo'tha jāyate |",
    "653:119": "śeṣai grahaiḥ krūraistu vividhaiścāpi kutsitaiḥ ||",
    "653:120": "jāyate dhūrttarāgārttaḥ vyādhibhiśca samākulaḥ |",
    "653:121": "nedadyustasya mantrā vai śāntikaṃ pauṣṭikaṃ param ||",
    "653:122": "kṣudrāṃ kaśmalāṃścaiva kravyādāṃ piśitāśinām |",
    "653:123": "krūrai grahamukhyaistu darśanāśca bhavet sadā ||",
    "653:124": "eteṣāṃ mantrasidhyarthaṃ krūrakarmeṣu yojaye |",
    "653:125": "niṣiaddhaṃ gamanaṃ tatra agrapañcavivarjitam ||",
    "653:126": "gamanāgamanayostatra na siddhiḥ sarvakarmasu |",
    "653:127": "kṣudrakarma tathā teṣāṃ dadyaḥ sarvato jānā ||",
    "653:128": "sitākhyau grahamukhyau tau pātakau dve pare'parau |",
    "653:129": "caturthā grahamukhyānāṃ darśanaṃ śreyasodbhavam ||",
    "653:130": "ubhau raktau ubhau kṛṣṇau darśanaṃ krūrakarmiṇām |",
    "653:131": "sitau śuklendumukhyau tau pītakau budhabṛhaspatau ||",
    "653:132": "arkāṅgārakaścaiva raktau tau diśi bhūmijau |",
    "653:133": "ṣaṇḍo rāho tathā kṛṣṇau vicitrā śeṣakā grahā ||",
    "653:134": "nānāgrahagṛhā proktā vicitrā dhātusubhūṣitāḥ |",
    "653:135": "vicitrākṛtayaḥ kecid vicitrapraharaṇodyatā ||",
    "653:136": "nānādhātugaṇādhyakṣā nānāṛṣipurātanai |",
    "653:137": "śiṣyante grahāṇāṃ sarvaṃ apsarābhiśca kinnaraiḥ |",
    "653:138": "gaganasthā varṇato yātā gatiyonividitā |",
    "653:139": "antarīkṣacarāḥ sarve nakṣatraiḥ sahacāriṇaḥ ||",
    "653:140": "vyomni dhānasamāyātā vicitrā gaticeṣṭitā |",
    "653:141": "maharddhikā prabhāvataḥ gatyā rūpaveṣasamāśrayāt ||",
    "653:142": "kathitā munivaraiḥ sarvaiḥ karmatattvārthayojitāḥ |",
    "653:143": "caturthe'hani saṃyuktāścatuḥsattvaniyojitāḥ ||",
    "653:144": "catvāro grahavarā proktā sito pīto'rthasādhakāḥ |",
    "653:145": "śeṣāḥ krūrakarmasu raktau kṛṣṇau ca yojitau ||",
    "653:146": "nācaret sarvakarmāṇi śāntikāni viśeṣataḥ |",
    "653:147": "kṛṣṇaraktau grahau hyetau tithau cāpi caturdaśī ||",
    "653:148": "nācaret sarvakāryāṇi kṣudrakarmāṇi sādhayet |",
    "653:149": "mānuṣe sādhayedarthī gaṇanāme śubhodayām ||",
    "653:150": "taireva kārayet kṣipraṃ āsanaṃ śayanaṃ sadā |",
    "653:151": "mandiraṃ ca viśeddhīmāṃ sarvadurgāṇi kārayet ||",
    "653:152": "karkaṭarāśijātastho dṛśyate manujāḥ śubhaḥ |",
    "653:153": "śāstā ca bhavet kṣipraṃ rājānaścakravartinaḥ ||",
    "653:154": "bhavante janmino bodho pūrvakarmasamudbhavaiḥ |",
    "653:155": "śukrendragrahamukhyānāṃ darśanaṃ caiva jāyatām ||",
    "653:156": "śubhe'hani śubhe deśe bodhisattva ajāyata |",
    "653:157": "puṣyanakṣatrayogena jāyante marupūjitā ||",
    "653:158": "buddhāstrailokyaguravo'nye'pi maharddhikāḥ |",
    "653:159": "rājyakarttā nikṛntā ca bahuprāṇinarādhipāḥ ||",
    "653:160": "jāyante vividhā loke śanyarkāṅgāracihnitāḥ |",
    "653:161": "kecijjanabhūyiṣṭhā martyā karmaparāyaṇā ||",
    "653:162": "jāyante vividhācārā puṣye jātāpi te sadā |",
    "653:163": "tasmāt karmaphalaṃ viddhi gatimātmānaceṣṭitā ||",
    "653:164": "kevalaṃ tu sadācārā grahakarmaniyojitā |",
    "653:165": "lokadharmānapekṣeha nirdiśanti tathā jināḥ ||",
    "653:166": "karma lokavaicitryaṃ lokadhātusamādhijam |",
    "653:167": "bhājanaṃ sarvalokanāmāśrayodbhavasambhavam ||",
    "653:168": "vicitraṃ kathitaṃ loke surāḥ ! śreṣṭhāṃ nibodhatām |",
    "653:169": "karmajaṃ hi purā pyāsī kathayāmāsa vatsalaḥ ||",
    "653:170": "sattvasādhāraṇā dhīmāṃ bodhisattvo maharddhikaḥ |",
    "653:171": "mañjughoṣastadā vavre sattvānāṃ hitakāmyayā ||",
    "653:172": "karmajaṃ kathitaṃ sarvaṃ mantratantrasavistaram |",
    "653:173": "eṣo vaḥ surāḥ sarve dharmo hyekena yaḥ sadā ||",
    "653:174": "karkaṭo rāśijātasya dadyānmantraṃ tu pauṣṭikam |",
    "653:175": "tataḥ pareṇa siṃhasya rāśirdṛśyati mānavām ||",
    "653:176": "siṃhajāto bhavenmartya aśūn lubdha eva tu |",
    "653:177": "strīśaṭho māṃsabhojī syād girikandaravāsinaḥ ||",
    "653:178": "senāpatya tathā nityaṃ kārayecca vasundharām |",
    "653:179": "mahīpālo mahādhyakṣaḥ krūrakarmā sadā śuciḥ ||",
    "653:180": "kṛtaghnaḥ kṛtamantraśca pāpakarmasadārataḥ |",
    "653:181": "mitradrohī sadā lubdhaḥ śaṭhaścaivamajāyata ||",
    "653:182": "grahaiścāpi sadā dṛṣṭā sitaiḥ pītaiśca dhīmataiḥ |",
    "653:183": "jāyate dhārmikastatra kṛṣṇaiścāpi śaṭhaḥ smṛtaḥ ||",
    "653:184": "tatra karma samuddiṣṭaṃ pauṣṭikaṃ siddhilipsitām |",
    "653:185": "uttiṣṭhaṃ khecaraṃ cāpi atimānasamodgatam ||",
    "653:186": "nānyaṃ karma samudvetaṃ samānaṃ cāpi varjayet |",
    "653:187": "tataḥ pareṇa siṃhasya kanyarāśiriti smṛtaḥ ||",
    "653:188": "tatra jāto bhaveddhūrtastaskaraḥ kṛpaṇaḥ śaṭhaḥ |",
    "653:189": "strīṣu kāntaḥ sadā lubdhaḥ krūraḥ sāhasikaḥ sadā ||",
    "653:190": "mūrkhaḥ paradārī ca stabdho mānonnataḥ sadā |",
    "653:191": "śubhanakṣatravāreṇa śubhadṛṣṭigrahoditaiḥ ||",
    "653:192": "pītaśuklairgrahairdṛṣṭā jāyante ca mahādhanāḥ |",
    "653:193": "śuddhamantraḥ sadā dhīmān śucivṛttisamāśraye ||",
    "653:194": "sambhūtā mantratantrāśca sādhayet mahītale |",
    "653:195": "kṣipramarthakarā ye tu puṣṭyarthā ye tu kīrtitā ||",
    "653:196": "sādhayenmantravit sarvāṃ jināṅgīkulayorapi |",
    "653:197": "jinendramukhyā ye mantrā bahudhā cāpi kīrtitā ||",
    "653:198": "sādhayenmantravit sarvāṃ rāśyartheṣveva jātiṣu |",
    "653:199": "tataḥ pareṇa bhaved rāśiḥ tulānāmani kīrtitā ||",
    "653:200": "prasiddhāṃ karmabhūyiṣṭhāṃ tannāsevet tadāśritām |",
    "653:201": "tulāyāṃ jāyate dhīmānmantrasiddhiṣu yojitaḥ ||",
    "653:202": "na kārayet sādhanāṃ sarvāṃ uttiṣṭhaṃ bhūnibandhanām |",
    "653:203": "sarvamantraprasiddhyarthaṃ gatiyoniṣu ācaret ||",
    "653:204": "dhūrtaḥ kṛpaṇo lubdhaḥ matsarī caiva jāyate |",
    "653:205": "tulāyāṃ rāśijātastho dṛśyate ca sadā rataḥ ||",
    "653:206": "taṃ kuryāt sadā mantrī tasmiṃ rāśau samāsṛtaḥ |",
    "653:207": "yaṃ na cācakṣate loke bhūmirarthārthasampadām ||",
    "653:208": "grahamukhye tadā jāto pītaiḥ śuklaiśca sarvataḥ |",
    "653:209": "na bhajenmantrasiddhiṃ ca yatnarakṣārthasampade ||",
    "653:210": "kṣaṇamātre tathā sarvaṃ sādhyantaṃ niyojitaiḥ |",
    "653:211": "śubhairgrahairyadā dṛṣṭaḥ pītaiḥ śuklaiśca sarvataḥ ||",
    "653:212": "mahātmā jāyate śūraḥ dhārmiko'tha narādhipaḥ |",
    "653:213": "krūratarairgrahairdṛṣṭaḥ śanyarkāṅgārasiṃhajaiḥ ||",
    "653:214": "tulāyā jātarāśyarthaḥ matsaro bhavate pumāṃ |",
    "653:215": "bahurogo daridraśca vyādhirogārtasamudbhavam ||",
    "653:216": "pracaṇḍaḥ sarvakarmeṣu krūraḥ sāhasikaḥ sadā |",
    "653:217": "na bhajecchāntikarmāṇi jinatattvāṅgabhāṣitam ||",
    "653:218": "raudraṃ kurute karmāṃ vajriṇe samudayoditām |",
    "653:219": "ābhicārukakarmāṇi nānāyuddhakṛtāni tu ||",
    "653:220": "tasmiṃ rāśau sadā tatra kule tatra samudbhave |",
    "653:221": "kutsitā jinavaraiḥ karma siddhimāyāti tatra tu ||",
    "653:222": "pradhānaguṇavistāraṃ prabhāvaṃ cāpi varjayet |",
    "653:223": "pravāsagamanaṃ caiva nācareddiśi māśujam ||",
    "653:224": "mandaraṃ vāhanaṃ cāpi sattvadhātukṛtākṛtam |",
    "653:225": "nācaret sarvakarmāṇi tasmiṃ rāśau divākare ||",
    "653:226": "vṛścikāttu samutpāde sattvayoni samāśrayet |",
    "653:227": "bhavate liṅgavaicitryaṃ kathyamānaṃ nibodhatām ||",
    "653:228": "tīvraḥ sāhasikaḥ krūro durdharṣo mānadarpitaḥ |",
    "653:229": "vakro lubdhastathā martyo jāyate vasudhātale ||",
    "653:230": "prājño dhārmiko vidvān vakraścaiva durāsadaḥ |",
    "653:231": "strīṣu kānto bhavenmartyaḥ kṛtajño dṛḍhaparākramaḥ ||",
    "653:232": "tantramantrasadodyuktaḥ sevāyāṃ gurupūjakaḥ |",
    "653:233": "darśanaṃ grahamukhyānāṃ śukracandrabudho guruḥ ||",
    "653:234": "praśastaṃ śreyasaṃ lakṣyaṃ āyurārogyavarddhanam |",
    "653:235": "teṣāṃ darśanasiddhyarthaṃ mantriṇāmūrdhvasādhane ||",
    "653:236": "śanyarkāṅgārakau rāhuḥ paśyati taṃ naraṃ yadā |",
    "653:237": "krūraḥ sāhasiko vakro jāyate raudrakarmakṛt ||",
    "653:238": "teṣāṃ ca vajriṇe mantrāḥ siddhyante krūrakarmiṇām |",
    "653:239": "nāgacchet sarvato martyo dineṣveva sukutsitaiḥ ||",
    "653:240": "tataḥ pareṇa dhanvākhyaṃ rāśimuktaṃ tathāgataiḥ |",
    "653:241": "jāyante bahudhā martyā gatideśasamāśrayāt ||",
    "653:242": "ante ca śobhanāḥ sarve bālyā duḥkhabhāginaḥ |",
    "653:243": "yathāvibhāganirdeśā āyuṣaḥ parikīrtitāḥ ||",
    "653:244": "tathā dhanārthaniṣpattiṃ vāciṣye arthasampadām |",
    "653:245": "svayoniṃ nāśayennityaṃ parayoniṃ vivarddhayet ||",
    "653:246": "vahapatyo bahubhāṣya bahurāgaratipriyaḥ |",
    "653:247": "asaṃyato bhavenmartyaḥ dhanūrāśisamāśrayāt ||",
    "653:248": "prabhuḥ śrīmāṃ sadā dakṣo dhārmiko vāpi jāyate |",
    "653:249": "darśanaṃ yadi mukhyānāṃ grahāṇāṃ sitapītakām ||",
    "653:250": "teṣāmācarenmantrā nānāpraharaṇodbhavām |",
    "653:251": "nānāśastraphalā vāpi vastrabhūṣaṇavāhanā ||",
    "653:252": "nānādhātukṛtāṃścaiva nānādhātuphalodbhavām |",
    "653:253": "siddhyante tasya mantraṃ vai munijuṣṭāṅgasambhavā ||",
    "653:254": "tataḥ pareṇa karmāṇi sarvadravyaistu kārayet |",
    "653:255": "prasavet sarvato mantrī gatideśaniratyayām ||",
    "653:256": "svālayaṃ vāhanam cāpi svasutāṃ ca niveśanam |",
    "653:257": "bhuṣajaṃ sarvamiṣṭaṃ tu mahārthaṃ cordhvagāminam ||",
    "653:258": "siddhaye tasya muktātmā kṣiprameva kare sthitā |",
    "653:259": "tataḥ pareṇa rāśyāyāṃ makarastho dṛśyate sama ||",
    "653:260": "teṣu jātaḥ sadā martyaḥ liṅgairetairhi lakṣayet |",
    "653:261": "mātṛbhakto pitṛbhaktaśca khyāto bahumataḥ prabhuḥ ||",
    "653:262": "duḥsahaḥ sarvaduḥkhānāmāḍhyo'pi dhanasañcakaḥ |",
    "653:263": "kṛpaṇo lubdhacittaśca śaṭhaścaivamajāyata ||",
    "653:264": "śukrendragrahadṛṣṭānāṃ sarvasampatti jāyate |",
    "653:265": "kṛṣṇaraktagrahā ye tu krūrakarmā tu pūrvavat ||",
    "653:266": "nāgacchet tatra mantrajñaḥ vidiśāṃ caiva sarvataḥ |",
    "653:267": "duṣṭāṃ sādhayet karmāṃ aniṣṭaṃ caiva varjayet ||",
    "653:268": "vamanagamanaṃ caiva uttarāṃ diśimāśrayet |",
    "653:269": "mahāsamudrārthagatāṃ dravyāṃ nauyānamāviśet ||",
    "653:270": "prāpnuyāt sampadāṃ tatra nimnamādhyakṣadeśajam |",
    "653:271": "tataḥ pareṇa kumbheti makarāt samuditāt paraḥ ||",
    "653:272": "kumbharāśisamākhyeyā sattvajātāśrayā sadā |",
    "653:273": "bahudhā bahuliṅgāstu kathitā te narottamaiḥ ||",
    "653:274": "vicitrā citrarūpāstu varṇajātisamāśrayāt |",
    "653:275": "śyāmavarṇo viśālākṣo jāyante bahumatā narāḥ ||",
    "653:276": "maithunāśaktavaste tu grāmyadharmārthacintakāḥ |",
    "653:277": "kṛtajñā dhārmikā proktā mantrajāḥ kumbharāśayaḥ ||",
    "653:278": "śuklapītā grahā dṛṣṭā loke'smin samprapūjitāḥ |",
    "653:279": "kṛṣṇaraktā grahā ye tu dṛṣṭajātisamodayā ||",
    "653:280": "vyaṅgā kṛpaṇayo mūrkhā capalāḥ taskarāvahā |",
    "653:281": "bahurogā daridrāśca jāyante mānavā sadā ||",
    "653:282": "teṣāṃ na kārayet karma uttamaṃ munipūjitam |",
    "653:283": "aṅgārthasambhavā yena dadyuḥ sarvakarmasu ||",
    "653:284": "na gacchet prāpya tīrāntaṃ ato naivāpi varṇitam |",
    "653:285": "kuryāt vajrakule karma mantrasiddhililipsayā ||",
    "653:286": "krūraṃ krūrakarmāntaṃ sphaṭ huṅkārabhūṣitam |",
    "653:287": "mantraṃ sādhayeccātra krodharājasuyojitam ||",
    "653:288": "siddhyante pāpakarmāstu raudrakarmāsu yojitā |",
    "653:289": "tataḥ pareṇa mīneti rāśiruktā tathāgataiḥ ||",
    "653:290": "tatrasthā mānavāḥ sarve dṛśyante bahuliṅginaḥ |",
    "653:291": "mīnarāśisamājātā rūpāṇyetāni samudbhavaiḥ ||",
    "653:292": "prabhurmānadhīḥ śrīmāṃ bhogasampacchatānvitaḥ |",
    "653:293": "prabhavaḥ sarvalokānāṃ jāyate'sau mahītale ||",
    "653:294": "kṣipramarthakaro dhīmāṃ narādhipo'tha ajāyata |",
    "653:295": "śukrendudarśanājjātaḥ bhavelloke narottamaḥ ||",
    "653:296": "darśanād budhajīvānāṃ dhanāḍhyo'thamajāyata |",
    "653:297": "prāṃśumūrttirviśālākṣaḥ strīṣu kānto bhavet sadā ||",
    "653:298": "bahvamitro narādhyakṣaḥ kuṭilaścaivamajāyata |",
    "653:299": "bahumitro'tha śukraśca jāyate mitravatsalaḥ ||",
    "653:300": "tataḥ pareṇa krūro vai grahamukhyo divākaraḥ |",
    "653:301": "paśyate yadyasau martyān śanirāhusu bhūmijā ||",
    "653:302": "tadā kaṣṭamiti dhvajaḥ krūraścaiva jāyate |",
    "653:303": "pūrvavat kathitā hyete grahāḥ kṛṣṇāntaśuklayoḥ |",
    "653:304": "kuryāt sarvakarmāṇi mīnarāśisamāśrayāḥ |",
    "653:305": "tatrasthaścandramāṃ paśyet sarvāṃścaiva sādhayet ||",
    "653:306": "ataḥ pareṇa rāśīnāṃ gajamānuṣamānuṣām |",
    "653:307": "gandharvā rākṣasā garuḍāścāpi pannagāḥ ||",
    "653:308": "teṣāṃ svarūpato jātigatideśamacihnitaḥ |",
    "653:309": "manā udbhavasteṣāṃ liṅgairevaistu lakṣayet ||",
    "653:310": "yathā sattvaprakṛtiśca tathā liṅgaṃ vibhāṣyate |",
    "653:311": "svamantrā bhāṣitā hyetaiḥ teṣāṃ caiva niyojayet ||",
    "653:312": "rāśayaḥ kathitā loke dvādaśaiva gaṇodbhavāḥ |",
    "653:313": "gaṇitā grahamukhyaistu nakṣatraistu niyojitāḥ ||",
    "653:314": "saṃkṣepāt kathitā hyete kathyamānātivistarā |",
    "653:315": "mānuṣāṇāṃ tadā cakre nakṣatre grahamaṇḍalaiḥ ||",
    "653:316": "ata ūrdhvaṃ tu devānāṃ ṛṣīṇāṃ ca maharddhikam |",
    "653:317": "jñānaṃ pravarttate tatra etanmānuṣaceṣṭitam ||",
    "653:318": "acintyā buddhadharmāṇāṃ jñānadṛṣṭi narottamām |",
    "653:319": "sādhayet sarvamantrajñaḥ rāśijātau samudbhavā ||",
    "653:320": "+ ranakṣatrāṃ tithayo nityaṃ śuklapakṣe samācaret |",
    "653:321": "siddhisteṣu sadā proktā kṛṣṇe kṛṣṇakarmiṇām ||",
    "653:322": "grahaiḥ sitaiḥ pītaiḥ dinaiścaiva samācaret |",
    "653:323": "śuklapūrṇagatā candre paurṇamāsyeṣu yojayet ||",
    "653:324": "pratipacchuklapakṣe tu tṛtīye caiva rocayet |",
    "653:325": "pañcamī saptamī caiva daśamyekādaśodbhavām ||",
    "653:326": "trayodaśyāṃ tathā śukle sarvakarmāṇi ācaret |",
    "653:327": "puṣṭyarthaṃ śāntiyogaṃ ca gamanāgamanaṃ śubhāśubham ||",
    "653:328": "ālokhyā mantratantrasthaṃ nṛtyagītaratiḥ sadā |",
    "653:329": "bhūṣaṇaṃ yānamāvāsaṃ kṣurakarmaṃ ca dhīmatā ||",
    "653:330": "prayoktāḥ sarvato vidvāṃ martyaiścāpi śrīmataiḥ |",
    "653:331": "bhogasampatsadāsiddhiriṣṭasattvasamāgamam ||",
    "653:332": "nirdiṣṭaṃ munimukhyaistu anya anyakarmāṇi anyataḥ |",
    "653:333": "dhanārthibhiḥ śrīmataiḥ kṣipraṃ kuryānmantrārthasādhanam ||",
    "653:334": "+ + + + + + + + + candraśukragururbudhaiḥ |",
    "653:335": "vārairgrahavarairdivyaiḥ supūjitaiḥ śucimaṅgalaiḥ ||",
    "653:336": "tithiyuktaiḥ samāsena nirdiṣṭaiścāpi bhāvayet |",
    "653:337": "ghorairghorarūpaistu grahairmantraistithibhiḥ sadā ||",
    "653:338": "ācared raudrakarmāṇi kṛṣṇe kṛṣṇakarmiṇām |",
    "653:339": "gatideśasamāsaṃ ca yuktimantrārthasādhane ||",
    "653:340": "grahā rāśyarthanakṣatrā tithayaśca samoditā |",
    "653:341": "karmasiddhiprabhāvaṃ ca niyamaṃ sarvakarmasu || iti |",
    "653:342": "bodhisattvapiṭakāvatasaṃkānmahāyānavaipulyasūtrād āryamañjuśriyamūlakalpāt saptadaśamaḥ paṭalavisarāt tṛtīyo jyotiṣajñānapaṭalavisaraḥ parisamāpta iti |"
}